Client Component Creation:
- Start with `'use client'` directive
- Use `useState` and React hooks
- Handle browser APIs with hydration safety
- Check `typeof window` for browser-only code
- Use `@use-is-client.ts` hook pattern
- Prevent hydration errors with proper checks